prompt_text: Describe your stay at a resort.
content_text: I described my theatre resort as a wonderful adventure full of lots of outdoor activities. #1 The hotel we stayed at was very, very comfortable. And it was suitable for budget. Besides that, the people you know at the at the hotel, at the places we went to were very friendly. They were very knowledgeable and also spoke different languages. Aside from that, I really enjoyed it. I really relaxed. It was a great vacation and I recommend it to anybody else looking to have a fun adventure at a low budget.
